Saving your visualizations

  • Export option Plotting window > Export > save as an image/ save as a pdf > png/jpg > click save > check files tab

  • ggsave() option

library(ggplot2)
library(palmerpenguins)

ggplot(data = penguins) +
  geom_point(mapping = aes(x=flipper_length_mm, y=body_mass_g, color = species)) +
  facet_wrap(~species)
